        { "type": "component", "title": "고정 헤더 + 히어로 슬라이더", "fullWidth": true, "html": "<div class='cl-wrap'><header class='cl-header'><div class='cl-header-inner'><a class='cl-logo'>Miracell</a><nav class='cl-gnb'><span>About Us</span><span>Product</span><span>Service</span><span>R&D</span><span>Newsroom</span><span>Customer Support</span></nav><div class='cl-header-right'><span class='cl-lang'>KR</span><i>|</i><span class='cl-lang'>EN</span><i>|</i><span class='cl-lang'>CN</span><span class='cl-hdr-sep'></span><span class='cl-auth'>로그인</span><i>|</i><span class='cl-auth'>회원가입</span></div></div></header><section class='cl-hero'><div class='cl-hero-bg'></div><div class='cl-hero-center'><span class='cl-hero-sub'>STEM CELL SPECIALIST</span><h1 class='cl-hero-title'>Miracell</h1><p class='cl-hero-slogan'>Standard of Stem Cell</p></div><div class='cl-hero-dots'><span class='cl-hdot is-on'></span><span class='cl-hdot'></span><span class='cl-hdot'></span><span class='cl-hdot'></span><span class='cl-hdot'></span></div></section></div>", "css": ".cl-wrap{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Malgun Gothic','맑은 고딕',sans-serif;line-height:1.5;color:#1a1a1a;overflow:hidden}.cl-header{background:#1a1a1a;color:#fff}.cl-header-inner{max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;align-items:center;padding:18px 40px;gap:24px}.cl-logo{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.06em;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;flex-shrink:0;cursor:pointer}.cl-gnb{display:flex;gap:32px;margin-left:auto;font-size:15px;font-weight:500}.cl-gnb span{cursor:pointer;opacity:0.85;transition:opacity 0.2s}.cl-gnb span:hover{opacity:1}.cl-header-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:11px;opacity:0.5;margin-left:24px;flex-shrink:0}.cl-header-right i{font-style:normal;opacity:0.4}.cl-hdr-sep{width:1px;height:10px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);margin:0 8px}.cl-auth{cursor:pointer}.cl-hero{position:relative;height:560px;overflow:hidden}.cl-hero-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a0a0a 0%,#1a0a2e 30%,#0d0618 60%,#0a0a0a 100%)}.cl-hero-center{position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;text-align:center;z-index:1}.cl-hero-sub{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.4em;opacity:0.45;margin-bottom:24px;font-weight:400}.cl-hero-title{font-size:64px;font-weight:300;letter-spacing:0.12em;margin:0 0 12px;text-transform:uppercase}.cl-hero-slogan{font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.25em;opacity:0.5;margin:0;font-weight:300}.cl-hero-dots{position:absolute;bottom:32px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);display:flex;gap:10px;z-index:2}.cl-hdot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.25);cursor:pointer;transition:background 0.3s}.cl-hdot.is-on{background:#fff}@media(max-width:768px){.cl-gnb{display:none}.cl-header-inner{padding:14px 20px}.cl-hero-title{font-size:40px}.cl-hero{height:400px}}" },
        { "type": "heading", "value": "② About Us 섹션" },
        { "type": "component", "title": "비전 텍스트 + 통계 카운터", "fullWidth": true, "html": "<section class='cl-about'><div class='cl-about-inner'><div class='cl-about-left'><p class='cl-about-vision'>미라셀은 생명을 존중하며<br>모두의 건강한 삶을 비전으로 추구하는<br><strong>줄기세포 전문 기업입니다.</strong></p><p class='cl-about-desc'>줄기세포와 세포치료 분야의 전문 기술과 임상 경험을 바탕으로 건강한 내일을 만들어 가겠습니다.</p></div><div class='cl-about-right'><div class='cl-counters'><div class='cl-ctr'><span class='cl-ctr-num' data-to='2009'>2009</span><span class='cl-ctr-sfx'>년</span><span class='cl-ctr-label'>설립</span></div><div class='cl-ctr-div'></div><div class='cl-ctr'><span class='cl-ctr-num' data-to='650'>650</span><span class='cl-ctr-sfx'>여 개</span><span class='cl-ctr-label'>고객 병원</span></div><div class='cl-ctr-div'></div><div class='cl-ctr'><span class='cl-ctr-num' data-to='23'>23</span><span class='cl-ctr-sfx'>건</span><span class='cl-ctr-label'>기술 특허</span></div></div></div></div></section>", "css": ".cl-about{padding:80px 0;background:#fff}.cl-about-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 40px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:60px}.cl-about-left{flex:1}.cl-about-vision{font-size:26px;line-height:1.7;color:#1a1a1a;margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:400}.cl-about-vision strong{font-weight:700}.cl-about-desc{font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:#888;margin:0}.cl-about-right{flex-shrink:0}.cl-counters{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0}.cl-ctr{text-align:center;padding:0 40px}.cl-ctr-num{font-size:52px;font-weight:800;color:#1a1a1a;letter-spacing:-0.02em;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}.cl-ctr-sfx{font-size:16px;font-weight:400;color:#999;margin-left:2px}.cl-ctr-label{display:block;font-size:14px;color:#aaa;margin-top:6px}.cl-ctr-div{width:1px;height:48px;background:#e0e0e0;flex-shrink:0}@media(max-width:768px){.cl-about-inner{flex-direction:column;padding:0 20px}.cl-ctr{padding:0 24px}.cl-ctr-num{font-size:36px}}", "js": "var nums=document.querySelectorAll('.cl-ctr-num[data-to]');nums.forEach(function(el){el.textContent='0';var target=parseInt(el.dataset.to);var dur=1800;var st=performance.now();function tick(now){var p=Math.min((now-st)/dur,1);var e=1-Math.pow(1-p,3);el.textContent=Math.floor(target*e);if(p<1)requestAnimationFrame(tick)}requestAnimationFrame(tick)})" },
        { "type": "heading", "value": "③ Service 섹션" },
        { "type": "component", "title": "서비스 3열 카드 + 회전 CTA", "fullWidth": true, "html": "<section class='cl-svc'><div class='cl-svc-card cl-svc-1'><div class='cl-svc-bg'></div><div class='cl-svc-txt'><h3>CellBanking</h3><p>면역세포, 줄기세포<br>추출 보관 서비스</p></div></div><div class='cl-svc-card cl-svc-2'><div class='cl-svc-bg'></div><div class='cl-svc-txt'><h3>Stemcell<br>Medical Platform</h3><p>줄기세포 시술 커뮤니티 플랫폼</p></div><div class='cl-svc-cta'><svg class='cl-ring' viewBox='0 0 120 120'><defs><path id='rp' d='M60,60 m-44,0 a44,44 0 1,1 88,0 a44,44 0 1,1 -88,0'/></defs><text><textPath href='#rp'>VIEW MORE · VIEW MORE · VIEW MORE · VIEW MORE · </textPath></svg><div class='cl-plus'>+</div></div></div><div class='cl-svc-card cl-svc-3'><div class='cl-svc-bg'></div><div class='cl-svc-txt'><h3>Medical AICC</h3><p>병원 업무 자동화를 위한<br>Medical AI 콜센터 솔루션</p></div></div></section>", "css": ".cl-svc{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);min-height:480px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Malgun Gothic',sans-serif}.cl-svc-card{position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-end;padding:40px 32px;cursor:pointer}.cl-svc-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;transition:transform 0.5s ease}.cl-svc-card:hover .cl-svc-bg{transform:scale(1.05)}.cl-svc-1 .cl-svc-bg{background:linear-gradient(170deg,#1a0a2e 0%,#2d1854 35%,#1a0a2e 70%,#0d0618 100%)}.cl-svc-2 .cl-svc-bg{background:linear-gradient(170deg,#200a30 0%,#3d1560 35%,#2a0d45 70%,#150828 100%)}.cl-svc-3 .cl-svc-bg{background:linear-gradient(170deg,#0d0618 0%,#1a0a2e 35%,#2d1854 70%,#1a0a2e 100%)}.cl-svc-1 .cl-svc-bg::after,.cl-svc-2 .cl-svc-bg::after,.cl-svc-3 .cl-svc-bg::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 60%,rgba(160,80,200,0.1) 0%,transparent 65%)}.cl-svc-txt{position:relative;z-index:2;color:#fff}.cl-svc-txt h3{font-size:28px;font-weight:800;margin:0 0 10px;line-height:1.3}.cl-svc-txt p{font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;opacity:0.55;margin:0}.cl-svc-cta{position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);z-index:3;width:120px;height:120px}.cl-ring{width:120px;height:120px;animation:cl-spin 18s linear infinite}.cl-ring text{fill:rgba(200,16,46,0.45);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;font-weight:600}.cl-plus{position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);width:54px;height:54px;background:#C8102E;border-radius:50%;display:grid;place-items:center;color:#fff;font-size:28px;font-weight:300;box-shadow:0 0 28px rgba(200,16,46,0.45)}@keyframes cl-spin{from{transform:rotate(0deg)}to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}@media(max-width:768px){.cl-svc{grid-template-columns:1fr}.cl-svc-card{min-height:220px}}" },
