        { "type": "component", "title": "최신 뉴스 리스트 + View More", "fullWidth": true, "html": "<section class='cl-news-sec'><div class='cl-news-inner'><div class='cl-news-hd'><h2>Newsroom</h2><button class='cl-news-more'>View More +</button></div><div class='cl-news-list'><div class='cl-news-row'><span class='cl-news-dt'>2026.04.06</span><span class='cl-news-badge'>공지</span><span class='cl-news-tit'>미라셀(주), 미국 FDA 510(k) '원심분리기+키트' 시스템 전체 승인</span></div><div class='cl-news-row'><span class='cl-news-dt'>2026.02.13</span><span class='cl-news-badge'>공지</span><span class='cl-news-tit'>[신년인사] 2026년 새해 복 많이 받으세요!</span></div><div class='cl-news-row'><span class='cl-news-dt'>2025.08.11</span><span class='cl-news-badge'>보도</span><span class='cl-news-tit'>미라셀(주), CGP 아카데미 개최</span></div><div class='cl-news-row'><span class='cl-news-dt'>2025.05.20</span><span class='cl-news-badge'>공지</span><span class='cl-news-tit'>사우디아라비아 시장 진출 — 현지 파트너십 체결</span></div><div class='cl-news-row'><span class='cl-news-dt'>2025.03.15</span><span class='cl-news-badge'>보도</span><span class='cl-news-tit'>유럽 재생의학 심포지엄 스마트엠셀 임상 결과 발표</span></div></div></div></section>", "css": ".cl-news-sec{padding:80px 0;background:#f9f9f9;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Malgun Gothic',sans-serif}.cl-news-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 40px}.cl-news-hd{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:24px}.cl-news-hd h2{font-size:28px;font-weight:800;margin:0;color:#1a1a1a}.cl-news-more{background:0;border:1.5px solid #1a1a1a;padding:10px 24px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;color:#1a1a1a;transition:all 0.2s}.cl-news-more:hover{background:#1a1a1a;color:#fff}.cl-news-list{border-top:2px solid #1a1a1a}.cl-news-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding:18px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0;cursor:pointer;transition:background 0.15s;font-size:14px}.cl-news-row:hover{background:rgba(0,0,0,0.02)}.cl-news-dt{color:#999;font-size:13px;flex-shrink:0;width:90px;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}.cl-news-badge{font-size:11px;padding:3px 12px;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:99px;color:#888;flex-shrink:0;font-weight:500}.cl-news-tit{color:#1a1a1a;font-weight:500;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}@media(max-width:768px){.cl-news-inner{padding:0 20px}.cl-news-row{font-size:13px}}" },
        { "type": "heading", "value": "⑥ Contact + Footer" },
        { "type": "component", "title": "연락처 CTA + 푸터", "fullWidth": true, "html": "<section class='cl-contact'><div class='cl-contact-inner'><div class='cl-contact-cta'><svg class='cl-contact-ring' viewBox='0 0 140 140'><defs><path id='cp2' d='M70,70 m-55,0 a55,55 0 1,1 110,0 a55,55 0 1,1 -110,0'/></defs><text><textPath href='#cp2'>CONTACT US · CONTACT US · CONTACT US · CONTACT US · </textPath></svg><div class='cl-contact-plus'>+</div></div><p class='cl-contact-txt'>문의사항이 있으신가요?<br>미라셀이 도와드리겠습니다.</p></div></section><footer class='cl-footer'><div class='cl-footer-inner'><div class='cl-footer-col'><div class='cl-footer-logo'>Miracell</div><p class='cl-footer-info'>미라셀(주) | 대표이사: 박재우<br>서울특별시 강남구 테헤란로 625<br>TEL: 02-6952-7010 | FAX: 02-6952-7014</p></div><div class='cl-footer-col'><h4>Quick Menu</h4><div class='cl-footer-links'><a>About Us</a><a>Product</a><a>Service</a><a>R&D</a><a>Newsroom</a></div></div><div class='cl-footer-col'><h4>Follow Us</h4><div class='cl-footer-sns'><span class='cl-sns'>N</span><span class='cl-sns'>Y</span><span class='cl-sns'>I</span></div></div></div><div class='cl-footer-bottom'>COPYRIGHT © Miracell ALL RIGHT RESERVED.</div></footer>", "css": ".cl-contact{padding:80px 0;background:#fff;text-align:center;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Malgun Gothic',sans-serif}.cl-contact-inner{max-width:600px;margin:0 auto}.cl-contact-cta{position:relative;width:140px;height:140px;margin:0 auto 24px}.cl-contact-ring{width:140px;height:140px;animation:cl-spin 18s linear infinite}.cl-contact-ring text{fill:rgba(200,16,46,0.4);font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:0.22em;font-weight:600}.cl-contact-plus{position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);width:60px;height:60px;background:#C8102E;border-radius:50%;display:grid;place-items:center;color:#fff;font-size:28px;font-weight:300;box-shadow:0 0 24px rgba(200,16,46,0.4);cursor:pointer;transition:transform 0.2s}.cl-contact-plus:hover{transform:translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1.1)}.cl-contact-txt{font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;color:#888;margin:0}.cl-footer{background:#1a1a1a;color:#fff;padding:48px 0 0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Malgun Gothic',sans-serif}.cl-footer-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 40px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr;gap:40px;padding-bottom:40px}.cl-footer-logo{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.06em;margin-bottom:16px}.cl-footer-info{font-size:13px;line-height:1.8;opacity:0.5;margin:0}.cl-footer-col h4{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 16px;opacity:0.8}.cl-footer-links{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}.cl-footer-links a{font-size:13px;opacity:0.5;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;color:#fff;transition:opacity 0.2s}.cl-footer-links a:hover{opacity:0.9}.cl-footer-sns{display:flex;gap:10px}.cl-sns{width:36px;height:36px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border-radius:50%;display:grid;place-items:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:border-color 0.2s}.cl-sns:hover{border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)}.cl-footer-bottom{border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);padding:20px 40px;font-size:12px;opacity:0.35;text-align:center}@media(max-width:768px){.cl-footer-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:0 20px}}" },
        { "type": "note", "value": "메인 페이지 전체가 '브랜드 인상(Hero) → 비전(About) → 서비스(Service) → 제품(Product) → 뉴스(Newsroom) → 연락처(Contact) → 기업정보(Footer)' 순서로 설계된 전형적인 기업 사이트 스토리 흐름. 모노크롬 기반에 브랜드 레드(#C8102E)가 CTA와 강조에만 사용됨." }
      ]
