    "subpages": {
      "title": "서브페이지 클론",
      "blocks": [
        { "type": "text", "value": "서브페이지는 배너 → 사이드 네비게이션 → 콘텐츠의 3단 구조를 일관되게 유지합니다. 아래는 주요 서브페이지를 100% 클론 코딩한 것입니다." },
        { "type": "heading", "value": "① 기업소개 (About Us)" },
        { "type": "component", "title": "서브페이지 공통 레이아웃 — 기업소개", "fullWidth": true, "html": "<div class='cl-sub'><div class='cl-sub-banner'><div class='cl-sub-banner-bg'></div><div class='cl-sub-banner-txt'><span class='cl-sub-cat'>About Us</span><span class='cl-sub-crumb'>Home&nbsp;&nbsp;→&nbsp;&nbsp;About Us&nbsp;&nbsp;→&nbsp;&nbsp;기업소개</span></div></div><div class='cl-sub-body'><nav class='cl-sub-nav'><a class='cl-snav is-active'>기업소개</a><a class='cl-snav'>CEO소개</a><a class='cl-snav'>연혁</a><a class='cl-snav'>오시는 길</a><a class='cl-snav'>CI</a></nav><div class='cl-sub-content'><h2 class='cl-sub-h2'>혁신적인 줄기세포 바이오 기술로,<br>건강한 내일을 만듭니다.</h2><p class='cl-sub-p'>미라셀은 생명을 존중하며 모두의 건강한 삶을 비전으로 추구하는 줄기세포 전문 기업입니다. 줄기세포와 세포치료 분야의 전문 기술과 임상 경험을 바탕으로 건강한 내일을 만들어 가겠습니다.</p><div class='cl-sub-gallery'><div class='cl-gal-item cl-gal1'></div><div class='cl-gal-item cl-gal2'></div><div class='cl-gal-item cl-gal3'></div></div></div></div></div>", "css": ".cl-sub{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Malgun Gothic',sans-serif;overflow:hidden}.cl-sub-banner{position:relative;height:220px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;overflow:hidden}.cl-sub-banner-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;background:#1a1a1a}.cl-sub-banner-txt{position:relative;z-index:1;color:#fff}.cl-sub-cat{display:block;font-size:32px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:12px;letter-spacing:0.02em}.cl-sub-crumb{font-size:12px;opacity:0.4;letter-spacing:0.04em}.cl-sub-body{display:flex;min-height:400px}.cl-sub-nav{width:220px;border-right:1px solid #e8e8e8;padding:24px 0;flex-shrink:0;background:#fff}.cl-snav{display:block;padding:14px 28px;font-size:14px;color:#888;text-decoration:none;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.15s;border-left:3px solid transparent}.cl-snav:hover{color:#1a1a1a;background:#fafafa}.cl-snav.is-active{color:#1a1a1a;font-weight:700;border-left-color:#1a1a1a}.cl-sub-content{flex:1;padding:48px 40px;background:#fff}.cl-sub-h2{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 20px;color:#1a1a1a}.cl-sub-p{font-size:15px;color:#888;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 32px;max-width:600px}.cl-sub-gallery{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:12px}.cl-gal-item{height:160px;border-radius:0}.cl-gal1{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e8e0d4,#c4b89c)}.cl-gal2{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#a8c4d8,#7498b8)}.cl-gal3{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#b8d4b8,#7aaa7a)}@media(max-width:768px){.cl-sub-body{flex-direction:column}.cl-sub-nav{width:100%;border-right:0;border-bottom:1px solid #e8e8e8;display:flex;overflow-x:auto;padding:0}.cl-snav{white-space:nowrap;border-left:0!important;padding:14px 20px;border-bottom:3px solid transparent}.cl-snav.is-active{border-left:0;border-bottom-color:#1a1a1a}.cl-sub-content{padding:32px 20px}.cl-sub-gallery{grid-template-columns:1fr}}" },
        { "type": "heading", "value": "② 연혁 (History)" },
        { "type": "component", "title": "연혁 타임라인 — 풀 클론", "fullWidth": true, "html": "<div class='cl-hist'><div class='cl-sub-banner'><div class='cl-sub-banner-bg'></div><div class='cl-sub-banner-txt'><span class='cl-sub-cat'>About Us</span><span class='cl-sub-crumb'>Home&nbsp;&nbsp;→&nbsp;&nbsp;About Us&nbsp;&nbsp;→&nbsp;&nbsp;연혁</span></div></div><div class='cl-hist-main'><div class='cl-hist-hd'><span class='cl-hist-en'>History<span class='cl-hist-rdot'></span></span><h2 class='cl-hist-ko'>연혁</h2></div><div class='cl-hist-tabs'><button class='cl-htab is-on'>2020's</button><button class='cl-htab'>2010's</button><button class='cl-htab'>2000's</button><button class='cl-htab'>1990's</button><button class='cl-htab'>1980's</button></div><div class='cl-hist-line'></div><div class='cl-hist-body'><div class='cl-decade-hd'><span class='cl-decade-dot'>•</span><span class='cl-decade-nm'>2020's</span></div><div class='cl-yr-row'><div class='cl-yr-num'>2026</div><ul class='cl-yr-list'><li class='is-bold'>· 미국 식품의약국 FDA 510(k) '원심분리기+키트' 시스템 전체 승인</li><li>· 허가번호 K250516 - SMART M-CELL PRP Concentration System</li><li>&nbsp;&nbsp;허가번호 K250518 - SMART M-CELL Bone marrow Concentration System</li></ul></div><hr class='cl-yr-sep'/><div class='cl-yr-row'><div class='cl-yr-num'>2025</div><ul class='cl-yr-list'><li class='is-bold'>· 세계 최초 빛 에너지 이용한 링거백 커버 '크로마엠셀' 개발</li><li>· BSC 정맥 주사의 항노화 효과 임상 진행 - 순천향대병원 공동연구</li><li class='is-bold'>· 발리 의료 특구 줄기세포 클리닉 센터 설립</li><li>· 인도네시아 바이오메디컬특구 줄기세포 치료센터 설립</li><li>· 유럽 재생의학 심포지엄 스마트엠셀 임상 발표</li></ul></div><hr class='cl-yr-sep'/><div class='cl-yr-row'><div class='cl-yr-num'>2024</div><ul class='cl-yr-list'><li class='is-bold'>· 글로벌 강소기업 선정 (중소벤처기업부)</li><li>· 보건복지부 장관 표창</li></ul></div><hr class='cl-yr-sep'/><div class='cl-yr-row'><div class='cl-yr-num'>2023</div><ul class='cl-yr-list'><li class='is-bold'>· 사우디아라비아 진출</li><li>· 벤처기업 인증</li></ul></div><hr class='cl-yr-sep'/><div class='cl-yr-row'><div class='cl-yr-num'>2022</div><ul class='cl-yr-list'><li class='is-bold'>· Smart M-Cell 해외 40개국 수출</li><li>· 국내 700여 병원 납품</li></ul></div><hr class='cl-yr-sep'/><div class='cl-yr-row'><div class='cl-yr-num'>2021</div><ul class='cl-yr-list'><li class='is-bold'>· NET 신기술 인증 (산업통상자원부)</li><li>· 의료기기 GMP 인증</li></ul></div></div></div></div>", "css": ".cl-hist{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Malgun Gothic',sans-serif;background:#fff}.cl-hist-main{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 40px 60px}.cl-hist-hd{text-align:center;margin-bottom:28px}.cl-hist-en{font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:#C8102E;letter-spacing:0.04em;position:relative;display:inline-block}.cl-hist-rdot{position:absolute;top:-2px;right:-9px;width:5px;height:5px;background:#C8102E;border-radius:50%}.cl-hist-ko{font-size:52px;font-weight:900;margin:4px 0 0;color:#1a1a1a}.cl-hist-tabs{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:14px;margin-bottom:28px}.cl-htab{padding:14px 44px;border:0;border-radius:99px;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;background:#f0f0f0;color:#666}.cl-htab.is-on{background:#C8102E;color:#fff}.cl-htab:hover:not(.is-on){background:#e4e4e4}.cl-hist-line{height:2px;background:#1a1a1a;margin-bottom:48px}.cl-hist-body{padding:0 20px}.cl-decade-hd{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;margin-bottom:40px}.cl-decade-dot{font-size:40px;line-height:1;color:#1a1a1a}.cl-decade-nm{font-size:48px;font-weight:900;color:#1a1a1a}.cl-yr-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:110px 1fr;gap:28px;align-items:start}.cl-yr-num{font-size:30px;font-weight:800;color:#1a1a1a;text-align:right;padding-top:2px}.cl-yr-list{margin:0;padding:0;list-style:none}.cl-yr-list li{font-size:15px;line-height:2.1;color:#777}.cl-yr-list li.is-bold{font-weight:700;color:#1a1a1a}.cl-yr-sep{border:0;height:1px;background:#e8e8e8;margin:20px 0}@media(max-width:768px){.cl-hist-main{padding:24px 16px 40px}.cl-htab{padding:10px 24px;font-size:14px}.cl-hist-ko{font-size:36px}.cl-decade-nm{font-size:32px}.cl-yr-row{grid-template-columns:70px 1fr;gap:16px}.cl-yr-num{font-size:22px}}", "js": "document.querySelectorAll('.cl-htab').forEach(function(t){t.addEventListener('click',function(){document.querySelectorAll('.cl-htab').forEach(function(b){b.classList.remove('is-on')});t.classList.add('is-on')})})" },
        { "type": "heading", "value": "③ 제품 상세 (Smart M-Cell)" },
        { "type": "component", "title": "제품 상세 페이지 클론", "fullWidth": true, "html": "<div class='cl-sub'><div class='cl-sub-banner'><div class='cl-sub-banner-bg' style='background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1a1a,#2a2a2a)'></div><div class='cl-sub-banner-txt'><span class='cl-sub-cat'>Product</span><span class='cl-sub-crumb'>Home&nbsp;&nbsp;→&nbsp;&nbsp;Product&nbsp;&nbsp;→&nbsp;&nbsp;Smart M-Cell</span></div></div><div class='cl-sub-body'><nav class='cl-sub-nav'><a class='cl-snav is-active'>Smart M-Cell</a><a class='cl-snav'>BmSC Kit</a><a class='cl-snav'>BSC Kit</a><a class='cl-snav'>Chroma M-CELL</a><a class='cl-snav'>Vacuum lock syringe</a></nav><div class='cl-sub-content'><h2 class='cl-sub-h2'>Smart M-Cell</h2><p class='cl-sub-p'>세포용원심분리장치 · 의료기기</p><div class='cl-spec-grid'><div class='cl-spec-card'><div class='cl-spec-icon'>🧬</div><div class='cl-spec-nm'>줄기세포</div><div class='cl-spec-desc'>골수 유래 줄기세포 분리</div></div><div class='cl-spec-card'><div class='cl-spec-icon'>💧</div><div class='cl-spec-nm'>성장인자</div><div class='cl-spec-desc'>PRP 성장인자 농축</div></div><div class='cl-spec-card'><div class='cl-spec-icon'>🔬</div><div class='cl-spec-nm'>SDF-1α</div><div class='cl-spec-desc'>줄기세포 귀소인자</div></div><div class='cl-spec-card'><div class='cl-spec-icon'>🛡</div><div class='cl-spec-nm'>백혈구</div><div class='cl-spec-desc'>면역 세포 분리</div></div><div class='cl-spec-card'><div class='cl-spec-icon'>🩸</div><div class='cl-spec-nm'>혈소판</div><div class='cl-spec-desc'>고농도 혈소판 추출</div></div></div><h3 class='cl-sub-h3'>LED 파장별 특성</h3><div class='cl-led-tabs'><button class='cl-led is-on' style='--led:#0066FF'>Blue</button><button class='cl-led' style='--led:#00AA44'>Green</button><button class='cl-led' style='--led:#FFAA00'>Yellow</button><button class='cl-led' style='--led:#DD0000'>Red</button></div><div class='cl-led-info'>Blue LED (460~475nm) — 여드름균 사멸, 항균 효과</div><h3 class='cl-sub-h3'>기기 사양</h3><table class='cl-spec-table'><tr><td>분류</td><td>세포용원심분리장치 (A47070.01)</td></tr><tr><td>정격전압</td><td>AC 100-240V, 50/60Hz</td></tr><tr><td>소비전력</td><td>Max 200W</td></tr><tr><td>치수</td><td>340 × 340 × 280 mm</td></tr><tr><td>중량</td><td>약 8.5kg</td></tr></table></div></div></div>", "css": ".cl-spec-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:16px;margin:32px 0}.cl-spec-card{text-align:center;padding:24px 12px;border:1px solid #e8e8e8;transition:transform 0.2s}.cl-spec-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px)}.cl-spec-icon{font-size:28px;margin-bottom:8px}.cl-spec-nm{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px;color:#1a1a1a}.cl-spec-desc{font-size:12px;color:#999}.cl-sub-h3{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin:40px 0 16px;color:#1a1a1a;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e8e8e8}.cl-led-tabs{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:16px}.cl-led{padding:10px 28px;border:2px solid var(--led);border-radius:99px;background:transparent;color:var(--led);font-size:14px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s}.cl-led.is-on{background:var(--led);color:#fff}.cl-led:hover:not(.is-on){background:color-mix(in srgb,var(--led) 10%,transparent)}.cl-led-info{font-size:15px;color:#555;padding:16px;background:#f9f9f9;margin-bottom:24px}.cl-spec-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:14px}.cl-spec-table td{padding:14px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid #e8e8e8}.cl-spec-table td:first-child{font-weight:600;color:#1a1a1a;width:140px;background:#fafafa}@media(max-width:768px){.cl-spec-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}}", "js": "document.querySelectorAll('.cl-led').forEach(function(b){b.addEventListener('click',function(){document.querySelectorAll('.cl-led').forEach(function(t){t.classList.remove('is-on')});b.classList.add('is-on');var colors={'Blue':'Blue LED (460~475nm) — 여드름균 사멸, 항균 효과','Green':'Green LED (525~530nm) — 색소 침착 개선, 피부 진정','Yellow':'Yellow LED (585~590nm) — 홍조 개선, 혈관 수축','Red':'Red LED (660nm) — 콜라겐 생성, 상처 치유'};var info=document.querySelector('.cl-led-info');if(info)info.textContent=colors[b.textContent]||''})})" },
        { "type": "note", "value": "모든 서브페이지가 배너(220px 검정) + 좌측 사이드 네비(220px, 활성 항목 좌측 3px 검정 보더) + 콘텐츠 영역의 3단 구조를 완벽하게 유지합니다. 이 일관성이 사용자의 위치 인식과 탐색 효율을 보장합니다." }
      ]
    },
